@martinshapes: " Like making sure I eat a balanced diet, getting all the nutrients my body needs to stay healthy, my mind needs to get outside and in the natural elements. I’ll call it vitamin N. My brain needs some vitamin N (for nature) from time to time." Catch Josh Martin next week on our Instagram stories as he walks through building a custom camper to celebrate his and his wife's 30th wedding anniversary.

#Carhartt #BacktotheLand #diy #camperbuild #workwear #outworkthemall
